sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant MM as ModelMesh Serving
    participant AuthProxy as Auth Proxy<br/>(kube-rbac-proxy)
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Storage as Storage Backend<br/>(PVC / DB / MinIO)
    participant KServe as KServe Model Server<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant Client as Client / Dashboard

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over MM,Storage: Flow 1: ModelMesh Inference Data Capture
        MM->>TrustyAI: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>HTTP/80 plaintext<br/>Inference payload (input + output)
        TrustyAI->>Storage: Persist inference data<br/>File I/O (PVC) / JDBC:3306 (DB) / S3:9000 (MinIO)
        Storage-->>TrustyAI: Write confirmation
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,KServe: Flow 2: On-Demand Explanation Generation (ODH only)
        Client->>AuthProxy: POST /explainers/local/shap<br/>HTTP/80
        AuthProxy->>TrustyAI: Authenticated request<br/>HTTP/8080 plaintext
        TrustyAI->>Storage: Load inference data
        Storage-->>TrustyAI: Dataset
        TrustyAI->>KServe: Inference request<br/>gRPC/HTTP2 plaintext<br/>KServe V2 protocol
        KServe-->>TrustyAI: Prediction response
        Note over TrustyAI: Compute SHAP values<br/>(multiple model queries)
        TrustyAI->>KServe: Batch inference requests<br/>gRPC (semaphore-limited)
        KServe-->>TrustyAI: Batch predictions
        TrustyAI-->>AuthProxy: SHAP explanation JSON
        AuthProxy-->>Client: Response
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over TrustyAI,Prom: Flow 3: Scheduled Metric Calculation & Publishing
        Note over TrustyAI: Quarkus Scheduler triggers<br/>every 5s (configurable)
        TrustyAI->>Storage: Load inference data
        Storage-->>TrustyAI: Dataset
        Note over TrustyAI: Calculate metrics:<br/>SPD, DIR, KS, MMD, Meanshift
        TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Publish to Micrometer<br/>Prometheus gauges
        Prom->>TrustyAI: GET /q/metrics<br/>HTTP/80<br/>Bearer token (SA)
        TrustyAI-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics<br/>(trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir, drift gauges)
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over Client,Storage: Flow 4: Data Upload & Management
        Client->>AuthProxy: POST /data/upload<br/>HTTP/80
        AuthProxy->>TrustyAI: Authenticated request
        TrustyAI->>Storage: Store uploaded data
        Storage-->>TrustyAI: Confirmation
        TrustyAI-->>AuthProxy: Upload result
        AuthProxy-->>Client: Response
    end
